## Limitations
The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all possible reasons for victims returning to abusers. The complexity of individual cases means that not all factors can be generalized. Additionally, the lack of recent data in some sources may not reflect the current trends or emerging factors influencing victims' decisions. Further research, including interviews with survivors and professionals in the field, would provide a more comprehensive understanding.